body_html:
@jiarenyf which version of TFLite are you using, can you use the benchmark tool to profile. If you are using an older version of TFLite then there was a severe regression in Conv: issue #15554 which has been fixed. TFLite performance on most models is better than tf-mobile.
Also can you include a model with the bug, I can help in debugging the performance issues.

body:
@jiarenyf which version of TFLite are you using, can you use the [benchmark tool](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/tree/master/tensorflow/contrib/lite/tools/benchmark) to profile. If you are using an older version of TFLite then there was a severe regression in Conv: issue #15554 which has been fixed. TFLite performance on most models is better than tf-mobile. 
Also can you include a model with the bug, I can help in debugging the performance issues.
